Fees. The Borrower shall pay to Agent fees in the amounts and at the times set
forth in that certain letter agreement between the Sponsor and Bank of Montreal dated as of
October 2, 2014 (as amended from time to time, the "Fee Letter"). The Borrower hereby
assumes all obligations of Sponsor on account of such fees and agrees to be bound by all terms
and provisions of the Fee Letter related thereto and to pay all such fees set forth in the Fee Letter
in accordance with the terms thereof.
